\fs42 \cf0 INGREDIENTS
\b0 \
3-4 cups caramelized onions (recipe below)\
5 cups beef broth\
Salt and pepper to taste\
6 toasted rounds of French bread\
1 cup freshly grated Parmesan cheese
\b \
\
